@startuml
actor User
participant "UI" as UI
participant "API" as API
participant "ScreeningService" as Service
participant "Database" as DB
participant "EventBus" as Events

== Schedule Screening ==
User -> UI: Fill screening form
UI -> API: POST /api/screenings
API -> Service: ScheduleScreening(dto)
Service -> DB: Insert Screening
Service -> Events: Publish(ScreeningScheduled)
Events -> Service: Trigger reminder setup
API --> UI: 201 Created
UI --> User: Show confirmation

== Complete Screening ==
User -> UI: Mark as completed
UI -> API: PUT /api/screenings/{id}/complete
API -> Service: CompleteScreening(id, dto)
Service -> DB: Update Status
Service -> Service: CalculateNextDueDate()
Service -> DB: Update NextDueDate
Service -> Events: Publish(ScreeningCompleted)
API --> UI: 200 OK
UI --> User: Prompt for results
@enduml
